    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Ex 3: 数字和数学计算]]></title>
    <link href="http://ruby.code.kekou.de//blog/2014/04/01/ex03/"/>
    <updated>2014-04-01T13:29:08+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://ruby.code.kekou.de//blog/2014/04/01/ex03</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我配置了 Notepad++，可以写完 ruby 之后一键执行，不用再开启命令行了。</p>

<!--more-->


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>puts "Calc the results of 3+5"
</span><span class='line'>puts 3+5
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>puts "And 3.0+5"
</span><span class='line'>puts 3.0+5
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>puts "And if it is true the 4 equals to 5"
</span><span class='line'>puts 4 == 5
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>puts "3/2"
</span><span class='line'>puts 3/2
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>puts "3.0/2"
</span><span class='line'>puts 3.0/2</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>输出</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>Calc the results of 3+5
</span><span class='line'>8
</span><span class='line'>And 3.0+5
</span><span class='line'>8.0
</span><span class='line'>And if it is true the 4 equals to 5
</span><span class='line'>false
</span><span class='line'>3/2
</span><span class='line'>1
</span><span class='line'>3.0/2
</span><span class='line'>1.5</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>其实，添加 PATH 之后直接用 irb 来代替 calc 应该可以的吧？</p>
]]></content>
