  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Ex 2: 注释和＃号]]></title>
    <link href="http://ruby.code.kekou.de//blog/2014/04/01/ex02/"/>
    <updated>2014-04-01T13:20:46+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://ruby.code.kekou.de//blog/2014/04/01/ex02</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><code>#</code> 的作用是注释，英文为 octothorpe 或者 pound character。</p>

<!--more-->


<p>一行中， <code>#</code> 之后的所有内容都不会被执行。</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>#This is comment.
</span><span class='line'>puts "You can see this." #While you will not see this
</span><span class='line'>#This will not run.
</span><span class='line'>#puts "This will not run."
</span><span class='line'>puts "This will run."</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>将会输出</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>C:\Users\Administrator&gt;ruby ex2.rb
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>You can see this.
</span><span class='line'>This will run.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
